name: Zelda Maker: Figma Office
description:
The Figma Office 7th floor in 8-bit.

To play this world, duplicate this file then install and run the Zelda Maker plugin https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/846537436529611787/Zelda-Maker 

To make your own Zelda worlds, duplicate this file, create a new Frame, and drag in the provided Components
